			<ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a134" TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts329" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts330">
				<ANNOTATION_VALUE>vos a eh eh un ven ikh bin alt, ven ikh bin in aza MATZAV vi yetst, un afilek a besern, iz geven a reyd vegn iberlebn?</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
